WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:04.150
Well, good morning, family, good evening

00:00:04.160 --> 00:00:06.550
wherever you are. I talk to people

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.150
all over the world, so I always say

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.390
morning. Thank you for joining us

00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:13.110
again tonight. We have some work

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:16.390
to do.

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:17.990
I don't even really know where to start

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.470
other than I just want to give God

00:00:20.480 --> 00:00:22.630
all the praise and

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:25.349
glory for what he's doing. As we see,

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:29.189
prayer changes things. We see Pam Bondi

00:00:29.199 --> 00:00:32.630
and the man saying that he wanted to

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:36.389
harm her, trying to pay $45,000, which

00:00:36.399 --> 00:00:40.950
was around—I saw 50 on the

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:44.310
wanted. As I have

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:46.630
been praying over this today, I have

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:51.350
more to share with you. The

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:54.069
Lord is revealing more to us, Diana and

00:00:54.069 --> 00:00:54.079
I, and

00:00:54.079 --> 00:00:56.790
my children. As we were driving

00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:58.940
around, I

00:00:58.940 --> 00:00:58.950
saw a

00:00:58.950 --> 00:01:02.310
football,

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:08.630
and Pam Bondi was holding a football, but

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:11.429
I didn't understand what I was seeing on

00:01:11.439 --> 00:01:13.910
the

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:20.310
19th. When I saw her

00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:23.910
holding the football,

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:25.670
I said, 'This looks like a

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:28.950
football, but it

00:01:28.950 --> 00:01:28.960
has layers.'It

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:31.429
transformed from a

00:01:31.439 --> 00:01:35.749
football to a pinwheel that had

00:01:35.759 --> 00:01:38.230
layers that looked

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:41.510
dark black and white. That's why I

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:43.190
said it looked like one of those

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:46.389
Hostess cupcakes. It had the frosting all

00:01:46.399 --> 00:01:49.830
in it, and it was

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:51.429
pinwheel-looking,

00:01:51.439 --> 00:01:53.749
and the football turned into that.

00:01:53.759 --> 00:01:56.310
The Lord said there are many layers to

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:57.910
this

00:01:57.920 --> 00:02:01.030
for her to expose.

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:08.150
She's going to expose this

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:10.630
darkness, but she needs a little bit

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:13.990
more information to nail the coffin

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:15.830
closed and make it a closed

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:19.190
case.

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:21.430
She has enough evidence that she's

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:24.070
going to run with this.

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:27.190
The Lord said because of what she

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:30.390
will expose, there will be a price on

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:32.229
her head.

00:02:32.239 --> 00:02:35.830
I saw a price tag of over

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:38.150
$50,000.

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:41.350
I saw the zeros, and I saw

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:46.309
not 45, but 50.

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:49.910
As I saw this red

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:51.509
list,

00:02:51.519 --> 00:02:55.350
I saw Alex Jones was going to expose

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:57.910
some things that were dark, and what he would say would

00:02:57.920 --> 00:03:00.630
be credible. I saw

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:04.630
Tucker Carlson on the list. I saw many

00:03:04.640 --> 00:03:09.110
judges on this hit list and people

00:03:09.110 --> 00:03:09.120
in

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:13.350
high authority—Giuliani. I

00:03:13.360 --> 00:03:17.190
saw many people on this list, and some

00:03:17.200 --> 00:03:20.470
of their names had more zeros than

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:22.070
others.

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:25.990
The Lord said, 'You must pray for

00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:29.430
their protection, for they are on a list

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:32.390
to be taken out, and you must intercede

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:35.589
for them, for this is bigger than you

00:03:37.350 --> 00:03:37.360
realize.'I

00:03:41.519 --> 00:03:44.869
saw foreign

00:03:44.869 --> 00:03:44.879
people—and

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:48.630
I can't go into all

00:03:48.630 --> 00:03:48.640
that—who

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:55.910
were funding this through crypto.

00:03:55.920 --> 00:04:09.547
That's all I'm going to say.

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:11.589
We're going to

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:13.429
continue to pray for them because the

00:04:13.439 --> 00:04:15.670
Lord said

00:04:15.680 --> 00:04:21.509
what was said today

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:27.189
was communication.

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:29.830
It's bigger than the man that

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:34.710
was caught today;

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:37.430
this is communication.

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:45.510
Why would they have this gambling ring?

00:04:45.520 --> 00:04:47.590
And why would some of these people who

00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:52.070
are worth millions participate in this?

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:56.070
They're already worth millions of

00:04:56.080 --> 00:04:56.950
dollars.

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:58.310
Why would they risk their

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:01.510
chance of going to prison

00:05:03.440 --> 00:05:06.310
for a couple million dollars

00:05:06.320 --> 00:05:12.230
for these big

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:15.189
people?

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:17.510
You are thinking too small. That's

00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:22.550
what the Lord said. Blackmail. Blackmail

00:05:22.550 --> 00:05:22.560
tapes, videotapes.

00:05:22.560 --> 00:05:24.950
The Lord said

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:28.950
videotapes

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.990
with them doing certain things with

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:38.230
certain young people.

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:40.230
Blackmail.

00:05:40.240 --> 00:05:42.790
'Do what we tell you to do or

00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:46.790
more will come

00:05:46.790 --> 00:05:46.800
out.'This

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:49.670
is deeper than what

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:51.749
you can ever

00:05:51.759 --> 00:05:55.670
understand. And the Lord

00:05:55.670 --> 00:05:55.680
said—and

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:58.790
that's all I will say about

00:05:58.790 --> 00:05:58.800
that—but

00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:02.230
you must know that it doesn't make

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:04.230
sense. You can play the video of what the Lord said.

00:06:08.800 --> 00:06:09.350
Yes, sir.

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:12.689
Go ahead, son.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:17.749
Just play it

00:06:17.759 --> 00:06:19.909
right there and show them what

00:06:19.919 --> 00:06:25.789
the Lord said. Football, baseball...

00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:30.550
oh, and sports people. And then he

00:06:30.560 --> 00:06:32.150
talked to us about LeBron James, and I

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:33.270
thought that was interesting. He said

00:06:33.280 --> 00:06:35.430
he'll retire soon. Everybody says, 'Well, of

00:06:35.440 --> 00:06:37.029
course he will.'No, I'm talking about

00:06:37.039 --> 00:06:38.249
something more to this.

00:06:44.479 --> 00:06:47.749
I saw the king

00:06:47.759 --> 00:06:51.029
be

00:06:51.029 --> 00:06:51.039
dethroned—the

00:06:51.039 --> 00:06:54.790
name King James.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:58.070
There's more to this,

00:06:58.080 --> 00:07:00.150
and it was not a

00:07:00.160 --> 00:07:02.150
good thing.

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:04.629
The

00:07:04.639 --> 00:07:06.150
Lord said he would be

00:07:06.160 --> 00:07:07.909
dethroned.

00:07:07.919 --> 00:07:10.629
A humbling is coming.

00:07:10.639 --> 00:07:12.550
I don't know

00:07:12.560 --> 00:07:14.550
what that means, but I saw a humbling

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:18.629
coming, a play on words.

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:23.110
I'm just telling you what

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:25.430
I saw.

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:28.309
There's something more to a dethroning

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:31.350
of a king who considers himself

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:33.255
way

00:07:33.265 --> 00:07:35.670
above the King of Kings, the

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:39.270
Lord of Lords, Jesus Christ. King James

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:40.870
Version, King—all this stuff

00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:42.309
was in

00:07:42.319 --> 00:07:44.309
the air. But the Lord said,

00:07:47.039 --> 00:07:49.510
'There's about to

00:07:49.520 --> 00:07:52.550
be something huge happen in the NBA. There's about to be something huge happen in the NFL and

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:54.469
the major league.'He said, 'Watch what

00:07:54.479 --> 00:07:58.070
I'm about to do in these

00:07:58.070 --> 00:07:58.080
areas.'So,

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:00.869
that's what we were praying over.

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:08.710
You see, it's

00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:12.070
bigger than you realize.

00:08:12.080 --> 00:08:13.990
The Lord said this

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:17.909
several weeks ago. He said, 'Pray

00:08:17.909 --> 00:08:17.919
for

00:08:17.919 --> 00:08:23.110
an exposing of dark things: NFL,

00:08:23.120 --> 00:08:25.589
Major League Baseball,

00:08:25.599 --> 00:08:29.029
and the NBA.'It will be

00:08:29.039 --> 00:08:32.630
in all these arenas. I saw major

00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:34.389
corruption.

00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:36.550
The Lord said it will be an

00:08:36.560 --> 00:08:38.070
uncovering. And that's what this

00:08:38.070 --> 00:08:38.080
pinwheel

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:40.630
is. And I'm telling

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:42.949
you, she had a football. I said,

00:08:42.959 --> 00:08:44.630
'What is this?'because we're not even

00:08:44.640 --> 00:08:45.670
talking about football; we're talking

00:08:45.680 --> 00:08:48.070
about basketball and some of this stuff.

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:50.710
But the Lord said there's deep dark

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:53.829
corruption. And if you go back to what I

00:08:53.839 --> 00:08:56.630
saw

00:08:56.640 --> 00:09:06.921
concerning the children,

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:35.190
consider the children

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:38.310
trafficking.

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:41.509
It's much deeper than most

00:09:41.519 --> 00:09:45.670
of you will ever realize.

00:09:45.680 --> 00:09:48.550
But as this happens,

00:09:48.560 --> 00:09:51.750
if we pray into this, the Lord

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:53.269
said he has a hand on it. I'm

00:09:53.279 --> 00:09:56.550
telling you, we will see revival break

00:09:56.560 --> 00:10:00.070
out in major sporting events.

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:05.829
I saw major key players having a

00:10:05.839 --> 00:10:09.030
major revival and the Holy Ghost

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:11.750
taking over the NFL,

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:13.670
NBA,

00:10:13.670 --> 00:10:13.680
and

00:10:13.680 --> 00:10:15.910
Major League Baseball. We're

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:18.310
going to see people that are going

00:10:18.320 --> 00:10:22.069
to get really radical for Jesus

00:10:22.079 --> 00:10:24.710
in the days ahead,

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:27.910
a major revival they will be used

00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:30.790
to bring forth. The Lord is going to

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:36.230
pour out his spirit on our sports.

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:39.350
People will idolize them like gods, like

00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:41.110
Michael Jordans and all the

00:10:41.110 --> 00:10:41.120
celebrities.

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:43.670
The Lord said he's

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:45.509
going to use that celebrity for his

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:48.069
glory for bringing in the harvest.

00:10:48.079 --> 00:10:50.710
Watch what he does with these

00:10:50.720 --> 00:10:53.750
young people. But even

00:10:53.760 --> 00:10:56.389
more so with

00:11:00.399 --> 00:11:03.190
the music

00:11:03.190 --> 00:11:03.200
industry—the

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:04.870
Lord said pray over the music

00:11:04.880 --> 00:11:06.870
industry. Pray over all this for

00:11:06.880 --> 00:11:08.630
there's an uncovering. Even

00:11:08.640 --> 00:11:12.150
when I told you I saw

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:14.949
a new Democratic woman being groomed by

00:11:14.959 --> 00:11:18.310
the devil, hand-selected by the devil,

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:21.590
I saw this woman being raised up and

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:25.670
appointed.

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:27.030
Even when I told you

00:11:27.040 --> 00:11:29.430
yesterday I saw this new pastor coming

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:33.110
to Australia—I keep seeing these

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:35.829
key figures. The Lord's

00:11:35.829 --> 00:11:35.839
hand-selecting

00:11:35.839 --> 00:11:37.030
people, and the devil's trying to

00:11:37.030 --> 00:11:37.040
hand-select

00:11:37.040 --> 00:11:39.030
people.

00:11:39.040 --> 00:11:41.350
It's interesting to me because I

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:43.990
keep seeing both sides. The

00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:45.910
Lord's showing me the devil

00:11:45.920 --> 00:11:48.630
picking people to try to cause

00:11:48.640 --> 00:11:52.150
great distraction and disruption

00:11:52.160 --> 00:11:54.389
in the move. And then you see God

00:11:54.399 --> 00:11:55.910
saying, 'I'm raising up

00:11:55.920 --> 00:11:57.269
these people. I'm going to raise up new

00:11:57.279 --> 00:11:59.910
men with great voices like David's,

00:11:59.910 --> 00:11:59.920
Hannah's,

00:11:59.920 --> 00:12:02.150
and Esther's, and they're

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:03.590
going to be prayer people. They're going

00:12:03.600 --> 00:12:05.590
to be the closers.'The Lord

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:07.190
keeps talking about all this, but then I

00:12:07.200 --> 00:12:09.590
keep seeing the enemy and he has his

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:11.670
plan. But we know who has the greater

00:12:11.680 --> 00:12:13.430
plan.

00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:15.670
Greater is he that is in us than he that

00:12:15.680 --> 00:12:18.069
is in the world. The Lord

00:12:18.079 --> 00:12:20.230
told us, 'You're about to see

00:12:20.240 --> 00:12:24.310
weather manipulation,

00:12:24.320 --> 00:12:26.870
weaponized weather more than what you've

00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:28.389
ever seen before.'He said that even

00:12:28.399 --> 00:12:32.310
last night with ice storms,

00:12:32.320 --> 00:12:36.150
winter cyclones, heavy

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:39.430
snowfall, blizzard conditions

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:42.550
in Buffalo, and lake effect snow that will

00:12:42.560 --> 00:12:45.750
be the largest we've ever seen. I'm

00:12:45.760 --> 00:12:49.269
talking about seeing major weather

00:12:49.279 --> 00:12:51.430
events in the days ahead. Well, you say,

00:12:51.440 --> 00:12:52.949
'Well, Brandon, we have weather events

00:12:52.959 --> 00:12:55.269
all the time.'Yes, but this is going to

00:12:55.279 --> 00:12:57.350
be different

00:12:57.350 --> 00:12:57.360
from

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:58.790
what

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:02.710
I saw. I saw major winds,

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:05.190
major straight-line winds, and power

00:13:05.200 --> 00:13:07.670
outages that would go for a thousand

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:10.150
miles.

00:13:10.160 --> 00:13:12.069
I'm talking about

00:13:12.079 --> 00:13:14.389
crippling ice storms.

00:13:14.399 --> 00:13:16.230
The Lord said, 'You have to pray

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:17.430
over the weather.'That's why I brought all

00:13:17.430 --> 00:13:17.440
that

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:20.230
up last night.

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:23.509
I was trying to encourage you to use

00:13:23.519 --> 00:13:27.350
your authority over drought

00:13:27.350 --> 00:13:27.360
and

00:13:27.360 --> 00:13:30.710
rain.

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:33.030
As he is, so are we in this world.

00:13:33.040 --> 00:13:35.110
The Lord was showing us:

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:37.670
'Brandon, if I can call peace to the

00:13:37.680 --> 00:13:39.269
storms, I've given you the ability to

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:42.389
pray over it also.'As he is, so are we

00:13:42.399 --> 00:13:44.389
in this world.

00:13:44.389 --> 00:13:44.399
I

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:45.430
just wanted to

00:13:45.440 --> 00:13:47.269
encourage you all when I showed you how

00:13:47.279 --> 00:13:51.030
much rain northern Oklahoma got, all

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:53.110
over Tulsa.

00:13:55.120 --> 00:13:57.110
Every time I call in a certain

00:13:57.120 --> 00:13:59.590
number, I say I'm waiting for over five

00:13:59.600 --> 00:14:04.550
inches of rain to come over our land,

00:14:04.560 --> 00:14:07.030
fill our rivers, our ponds,

00:14:07.040 --> 00:14:09.509
our creeks, and our

00:14:09.519 --> 00:14:12.470
lakes so that we don't have a drought. We

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:14.470
take authority over drought. We call the

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:17.110
rain in Jesus'name. You

00:14:17.120 --> 00:14:19.509
have authority to do that. Pray over

00:14:19.519 --> 00:14:22.710
your weather.

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:31.150
There it is, right there.

00:14:37.199 --> 00:14:39.509
Everywhere in Tulsa,

00:14:39.519 --> 00:14:41.990
the rain came. That's what the Lord

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:43.829
was trying to show

00:14:43.839 --> 00:14:45.750
you.

00:14:45.760 --> 00:14:48.629
You can do that to your town. You can

00:14:48.639 --> 00:14:50.870
call in the rain. That's why I

00:14:50.870 --> 00:14:50.880
was

00:14:50.880 --> 00:14:54.150
praying over Australia, because I saw a great

00:14:54.160 --> 00:14:57.110
drought and that even the kangaroos

00:14:57.120 --> 00:14:59.350
would die because there's no water. I

00:14:59.360 --> 00:15:01.590
saw the lakes and the

00:15:01.600 --> 00:15:03.750
ponds

00:15:03.760 --> 00:15:05.829
completely dry

00:15:05.839 --> 00:15:08.790
with big cracks, and the land

00:15:08.800 --> 00:15:11.110
was like tumbleweeds blowing across. It

00:15:11.120 --> 00:15:13.350
was so bad. The Lord said, 'Pray for

00:15:13.360 --> 00:15:15.509
the rain.

00:15:15.519 --> 00:15:17.269
Pray for the rain.'That's what I

00:15:17.279 --> 00:15:19.269
was trying to show you.

00:15:21.360 --> 00:15:23.350
We started calling

00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:25.189
it in because we hadn't had rain in

00:15:25.199 --> 00:15:27.110
September, October, or November. Hey

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:30.069
sweetie, you want to come sit by me?

00:15:30.079 --> 00:15:31.670
I'll get out and then you can come

00:15:31.680 --> 00:15:35.670
sit down. I have my buddy.

00:15:35.680 --> 00:15:37.189
Sorry, I didn't want to disturb you.

00:15:37.519 --> 00:15:38.629
You're good.

00:15:38.639 --> 00:15:45.110
Come sit down by me.

00:15:47.120 --> 00:15:53.110
You look so marvelous.

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:55.350
So, we're just talking

00:15:55.360 --> 00:15:56.629
about all the rain and everything. We

00:15:56.639 --> 00:15:58.790
were praying over the rain,

00:15:58.800 --> 00:16:02.150
believing God for supernatural rain. If

00:16:02.160 --> 00:16:03.590
you ever read anything, you hold it out

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:06.069
of your mouth, don't you?

00:16:06.079 --> 00:16:08.389
Well, you can read about the blood. I

00:16:08.389 --> 00:16:08.399
have

00:16:08.399 --> 00:16:09.910
the book. We read that book last

00:16:09.920 --> 00:16:11.590
night. When you

00:16:11.600 --> 00:16:12.949
started reading, I felt the presence of

00:16:12.959 --> 00:16:15.990
the Lord. Did you? I

00:16:16.000 --> 00:16:17.110
don't know if they did,

00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:19.226
but I did. That's all that matters.

00:16:20.480 --> 00:16:22.790
But I'm reading about the precious blood

00:16:22.800 --> 00:16:25.269
of Jesus. You know, these little pocketbooks

00:16:25.269 --> 00:16:25.279
you can

00:16:25.279 --> 00:16:27.430
get for a buck.

00:16:27.440 --> 00:16:30.710
I love reading

00:16:30.720 --> 00:16:33.269
stuff like that, filling

00:16:33.279 --> 00:16:34.710
yourself up and being

00:16:34.720 --> 00:16:36.710
controlled by the Holy Ghost. We

00:16:36.720 --> 00:16:38.629
were listening to Corrie ten Boom today,

00:16:41.680 --> 00:16:43.110
and

00:16:47.680 --> 00:16:50.949
it

00:16:50.959 --> 00:16:53.189
was wonderful.

00:16:53.199 --> 00:16:55.430
It was on YouTube and

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:59.509
it blessed me. It

00:16:59.519 --> 00:17:03.030
made me really go deep inside of myself

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:06.390
to say, 'Listen, you've got to

00:17:06.400 --> 00:17:07.750
come up

00:17:08.799 --> 00:17:11.350
higher.'Beautiful.

00:17:12.799 --> 00:17:14.949
She challenged me,

00:17:14.959 --> 00:17:17.029
this lady did. We didn't even finish it,

00:17:17.039 --> 00:17:19.029
but

00:17:19.039 --> 00:17:21.110
I just want to encourage everyone

00:17:21.110 --> 00:17:21.120
to

00:17:21.120 --> 00:17:22.870
find things that will inspire

00:17:22.880 --> 00:17:24.870
you.

00:17:24.880 --> 00:17:27.750
Find things that will fan your flame to

00:17:27.760 --> 00:17:30.789
keep that fire going. Don't

00:17:30.799 --> 00:17:34.150
wait on your pastor or whoever

00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:36.150
is over you that

00:17:36.150 --> 00:17:36.160
you

00:17:36.160 --> 00:17:38.070
listen to. Don't wait on them to

00:17:38.080 --> 00:17:39.909
feed you Wednesdays and Sundays or

00:17:39.909 --> 00:17:39.919
whenever

00:17:39.919 --> 00:17:42.310
you go to church. You've got to

00:17:42.320 --> 00:17:44.710
have that

00:17:44.710 --> 00:17:44.720
bulldog-on-a-bone

00:17:44.720 --> 00:17:47.110
faith to say, 'Hey, I'm going

00:17:47.120 --> 00:17:48.710
to feed myself. I've got to get out

00:17:48.720 --> 00:17:50.470
there and get a hold of something. I

00:17:50.480 --> 00:17:53.990
cannot wait for somebody to

00:17:53.990 --> 00:17:54.000
spoon-feed

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:56.230
me. I've got to have enough to be a

00:17:56.240 --> 00:17:57.830
scavenger.

00:17:57.840 --> 00:18:00.070
I'm going to find something and

00:18:00.080 --> 00:18:02.390
live by faith, and

00:18:02.400 --> 00:18:04.789
I don't need somebody else to

00:18:04.799 --> 00:18:06.549
feed me. I'm going to feed

00:18:06.549 --> 00:18:06.559
myself.'That's

00:18:06.559 --> 00:18:08.070
what Diana and I have always done.

00:18:08.080 --> 00:18:09.669
When Megan was first

00:18:09.679 --> 00:18:11.830
diagnosed with autism, we couldn't

00:18:11.840 --> 00:18:13.270
really go to church

00:18:13.280 --> 00:18:15.510
because it was such a distraction.

00:18:18.880 --> 00:18:20.789
For all those years, we just

00:18:20.799 --> 00:18:22.150
learned how to feed ourselves. We

00:18:22.160 --> 00:18:25.270
fought. I

00:18:25.280 --> 00:18:27.350
said we're going to keep going

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:29.430
with this and we're going to find the

00:18:29.440 --> 00:18:32.150
word for whatever we need.

00:18:32.160 --> 00:18:33.750
A lot

00:18:33.760 --> 00:18:36.630
of times, it was always Kenneth E. Hagin. I

00:18:36.640 --> 00:18:38.150
listen to Brother Hagin most

00:18:38.150 --> 00:18:38.160
of

00:18:38.160 --> 00:18:40.070
all,

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:43.830
and then to the

00:18:43.840 --> 00:18:45.750
people we listen to now.

00:18:45.760 --> 00:18:48.710
Just keep fanning that flame.

00:18:48.720 --> 00:18:51.669
Listen to Lynn Hammond. Stir up how to

00:18:51.679 --> 00:18:54.549
pray in the spirit. How bad do

00:18:54.559 --> 00:18:57.430
you want change in your life? How

00:18:57.440 --> 00:18:59.830
hungry

00:18:59.830 --> 00:18:59.840
and

00:18:59.840 --> 00:19:02.390
desperate are you for change?

00:19:02.400 --> 00:19:05.430
Are you willing to go out

00:19:05.440 --> 00:19:07.110
and look for something versus sitting

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:08.549
there waiting? I'm telling you,

00:19:08.559 --> 00:19:10.630
it comes to the point where I see a lot

00:19:10.640 --> 00:19:12.549
of these people say, 'Brandon, I

00:19:12.559 --> 00:19:13.669
need all

00:19:13.669 --> 00:19:13.679
this.'Get

00:19:13.679 --> 00:19:17.510
it. Be a contender. Fight for

00:19:17.520 --> 00:19:19.430
it. Nobody's going to just give it to

00:19:19.440 --> 00:19:22.390
you. You have to want it bad enough.

00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:24.630
I want change. I want the Holy Ghost in

00:19:24.640 --> 00:19:26.549
my life. I want the glory and the

00:19:26.559 --> 00:19:29.350
presence. I want Jesus manifested in my

00:19:29.360 --> 00:19:31.430
home so that whenever I have an issue,

00:19:31.440 --> 00:19:33.110
when you're

00:19:33.120 --> 00:19:34.950
overcoming something, when you get a bad report,

00:19:34.950 --> 00:19:34.960
or

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:37.029
when you have a bill

00:19:37.039 --> 00:19:39.350
you can't pay and

00:19:39.360 --> 00:19:41.750
the creditors are calling,

00:19:41.750 --> 00:19:41.760
you

00:19:41.760 --> 00:19:43.350
know

00:19:43.360 --> 00:19:46.230
what to do.

00:19:46.240 --> 00:19:48.070
If you have a need, you sow a

00:19:48.080 --> 00:19:50.310
seed. That's what we

00:19:50.320 --> 00:19:52.789
learned.

00:19:52.799 --> 00:19:55.430
He said he gives you wisdom to get

00:19:55.440 --> 00:19:57.590
wealth. So, we believe God and he gives

00:19:57.600 --> 00:20:00.630
us wisdom to make money. But what

00:20:00.640 --> 00:20:02.230
happens if you need a doctor's report?

00:20:02.240 --> 00:20:04.549
You find

00:20:04.559 --> 00:20:06.789
scripture. That's what we always do. We

00:20:06.799 --> 00:20:08.710
go back to the word.

00:20:08.720 --> 00:20:10.789
Find scriptures that

00:20:10.799 --> 00:20:13.430
pertain to what you're believing for and

00:20:13.440 --> 00:20:16.070
quote those scriptures over your life.

00:20:16.080 --> 00:20:18.789
We have Bibles everywhere. Diana

00:20:18.799 --> 00:20:20.230
got

00:20:20.240 --> 00:20:22.310
a waterproof Bible.

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:24.070
I thought that was perfect for the end

00:20:24.080 --> 00:20:25.830
times. You could hide it in the woods.

00:20:25.840 --> 00:20:26.310
The

00:20:26.320 --> 00:20:28.470
Antichrist is going to take

00:20:28.480 --> 00:20:29.750
everybody's Bible away. I don't even

00:20:29.760 --> 00:20:31.669
think that would burn.

00:20:35.120 --> 00:20:37.029
I just know we're in a time like

00:20:37.039 --> 00:20:39.909
we've never seen before, and

00:20:39.919 --> 00:20:41.510
it's going to keep

00:20:41.520 --> 00:20:43.990
increasing.

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:47.270
As of the 23rd, I

00:20:47.280 --> 00:20:49.909
know there is an acceleration,

00:20:49.909 --> 00:20:49.919
and

00:20:49.919 --> 00:20:51.909
we're about to see things

00:20:51.919 --> 00:20:54.710
we've never seen before. I have

00:20:54.720 --> 00:20:56.710
an urgency to come on here all the time

00:20:56.720 --> 00:20:59.029
to pray and to tell you all that Jesus

00:20:59.039 --> 00:21:00.789
Christ is coming and you've got to get your

00:21:00.799 --> 00:21:01.990
house in order. People ask, 'What does

00:21:02.000 --> 00:21:03.190
that mean,

00:21:03.190 --> 00:21:03.200
Brandon?'Well,

00:21:03.200 --> 00:21:04.950
what does that

00:21:04.960 --> 00:21:07.190
feel like to you? What is the Lord

00:21:07.200 --> 00:21:08.789
telling you to do?

00:21:08.799 --> 00:21:11.029
Do you

00:21:11.039 --> 00:21:12.870
have an urgency in your spirit to draw

00:21:12.880 --> 00:21:15.909
close to him?

00:21:15.919 --> 00:21:20.470
Does he know you?

00:21:20.480 --> 00:21:23.669
If you were to have a

00:21:23.679 --> 00:21:25.430
face-to-face encounter with the Lord,

00:21:25.440 --> 00:21:28.230
would he say, 'I know them'?

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:30.630
Or would he say, "You know, you may

00:21:30.640 --> 00:21:32.710
know a lot about the Father, but does he

00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:37.669
know you?

00:21:37.679 --> 00:21:40.470
Do you just go and visit once a

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:43.270
month or once a year at church, or do you

00:21:43.280 --> 00:21:44.710
have a relationship every single day

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:47.029
with him?"If I only had a relationship

00:21:47.039 --> 00:21:49.990
with Diana every

00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:52.230
month or every year, there

00:21:52.240 --> 00:21:54.470
wouldn't be a good marriage. A marriage

00:21:54.480 --> 00:21:57.029
is based on having a relationship every

00:21:57.039 --> 00:21:59.350
single day. We talk, we have communion.

00:21:59.360 --> 00:22:00.630
That's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:22:00.640 --> 00:22:02.390
That's the way it is with the Father.

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:04.390
You must have a relationship with him and

00:22:04.400 --> 00:22:06.310
find things that will inspire you to

00:22:06.320 --> 00:22:10.230
keep going: books, tape series,

00:22:10.240 --> 00:22:11.909
whatever. Back in the day, I

00:22:11.919 --> 00:22:13.510
used to buy a tape series every single

00:22:13.520 --> 00:22:16.230
time I got paid. I'd find a tape

00:22:16.240 --> 00:22:17.830
series and I'd listen to that one tape

00:22:17.840 --> 00:22:19.190
series the whole time because we only

00:22:19.200 --> 00:22:21.669
got paid every two weeks. I said if

00:22:21.679 --> 00:22:22.870
I could listen to it every

00:22:22.880 --> 00:22:24.630
time, whether

00:22:24.640 --> 00:22:26.950
it would be usually Lester

00:22:26.950 --> 00:22:26.960
Sumrall

00:22:26.960 --> 00:22:28.470
or somebody like that, I'd

00:22:28.480 --> 00:22:29.909
find something and think, "Man, I want to

00:22:29.919 --> 00:22:31.990
listen to these

00:22:31.990 --> 00:22:32.000
old-timers."I

00:22:32.000 --> 00:22:33.669
would listen to that whole tape series

00:22:33.679 --> 00:22:35.430
for two weeks and then

00:22:35.430 --> 00:22:35.440
I'd

00:22:35.440 --> 00:22:38.549
alternate them out just

00:22:38.559 --> 00:22:40.950
continually. Faith cometh by hearing, and

00:22:40.960 --> 00:22:43.029
hearing by the word of God. The only

00:22:43.039 --> 00:22:45.110
way you're going to get strong is

00:22:45.120 --> 00:22:46.950
with your faith growing. But faith works

00:22:46.960 --> 00:22:50.070
by love, so you've got to keep strife out.

00:22:50.080 --> 00:22:52.789
I'm telling you,

00:22:52.799 --> 00:22:56.549
it's like seeing an engine

00:22:56.549 --> 00:22:56.559
where

00:22:56.559 --> 00:22:59.190
the pistons and all the parts are

00:22:59.200 --> 00:23:01.110
moving in the engine so that you go

00:23:01.120 --> 00:23:03.750
really fast. But if one thing is off,

00:23:03.760 --> 00:23:06.230
that engine is not going to work right.

00:23:06.240 --> 00:23:07.350
That's the way it is in the spirit

00:23:07.360 --> 00:23:09.909
realm. You've got to make sure all

00:23:09.909 --> 00:23:09.919
those

00:23:09.919 --> 00:23:11.510
pistons are firing and all that

00:23:11.520 --> 00:23:13.750
stuff in the spirit is firing and going

00:23:13.750 --> 00:23:13.760
perfectly

00:23:13.760 --> 00:23:15.830
so that you're going

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:18.149
forward in your spiritual walk. That's

00:23:18.159 --> 00:23:20.310
going to make that spiritual car go

00:23:20.320 --> 00:23:22.710
forward. If not, you're going to be idle

00:23:22.720 --> 00:23:23.750
and sitting by,

00:23:23.760 --> 00:23:25.750
asking,

00:23:25.760 --> 00:23:27.430
"Why am I still this way after

00:23:27.440 --> 00:23:29.110
all these years? How come nothing's

00:23:29.120 --> 00:23:30.870
changed?"Most

00:23:30.880 --> 00:23:35.190
people keep doing the same

00:23:35.200 --> 00:23:37.430
thing expecting different results, and

00:23:37.440 --> 00:23:38.870
that's the definition of

00:23:38.880 --> 00:23:41.430
insanity. That's why I

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:44.149
say if it isn't working after 30 days,

00:23:44.149 --> 00:23:44.159
or

00:23:44.159 --> 00:23:46.390
if it isn't working after 60 days,

00:23:46.390 --> 00:23:46.400
we've

00:23:46.400 --> 00:23:50.390
got to make some changes in here.

00:23:50.400 --> 00:23:51.750
If what you're doing

00:23:51.750 --> 00:23:51.760
isn't

00:23:51.760 --> 00:23:53.669
getting you closer to God after a

00:23:53.679 --> 00:23:55.029
couple of weeks and you're saying,

00:23:55.039 --> 00:23:57.669
"Well, I'm still idly sitting

00:23:57.669 --> 00:23:57.679
by,"the

00:23:57.679 --> 00:23:59.669
Bible says if we draw nigh to him,

00:23:59.669 --> 00:23:59.679
he'll

00:23:59.679 --> 00:24:01.510
draw nigh to us.

00:24:01.520 --> 00:24:04.549
So I'm just looking, "Father, I want

00:24:04.559 --> 00:24:08.630
more. I'm desperate, I'm hungry, I'm

00:24:08.630 --> 00:24:08.640
thirsty."For

00:24:08.640 --> 00:24:10.950
you said those that

00:24:10.960 --> 00:24:12.549
hunger and thirst after righteousness

00:24:12.549 --> 00:24:12.559
shall

00:24:12.559 --> 00:24:14.950
be filled. I believe with all

00:24:14.960 --> 00:24:17.029
my heart that my wife and I

00:24:17.029 --> 00:24:17.039
are

00:24:17.039 --> 00:24:19.190
hungry, thirsty,

00:24:19.190 --> 00:24:19.200
and

00:24:19.200 --> 00:24:21.430
desperate. For the eyes of the Lord are

00:24:21.440 --> 00:24:23.269
running to and fro throughout the whole

00:24:23.279 --> 00:24:25.669
earth, looking for a heart who's perfect

00:24:25.679 --> 00:24:27.830
towards him.

00:24:27.840 --> 00:24:30.310
If the eyes of the Lord are running to

00:24:30.320 --> 00:24:32.630
and fro throughout the whole earth,

00:24:32.640 --> 00:24:33.990
looking for a heart who's perfect

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:37.830
towards him, let his eyes rest on me.

00:24:37.840 --> 00:24:39.350
Help me, O Lord, to have a perfect

00:24:39.360 --> 00:24:41.669
heart. Create in me a clean heart,

00:24:41.679 --> 00:24:43.350
Lord, so

00:24:43.350 --> 00:24:43.360
that you

00:24:43.360 --> 00:24:45.750
can look at me and say, "Hey,

00:24:45.760 --> 00:24:47.830
I want to go and visit his

00:24:47.830 --> 00:24:47.840
house."I

00:24:47.840 --> 00:24:53.350
make him feel comfortable in my home.

00:24:53.360 --> 00:24:55.430
I create an atmosphere of

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:57.909
worship in the house. I usually have

00:24:57.919 --> 00:24:59.669
worship playing all the time on the TV.

00:24:59.679 --> 00:25:01.830
I said, "Man, if Jesus showed

00:25:01.840 --> 00:25:03.430
up right now, would he be happy to be

00:25:05.750 --> 00:25:05.760
here?"Or

00:25:08.320 --> 00:25:11.029
would

00:25:11.039 --> 00:25:13.990
he go, "You know what? I look at the

00:25:14.000 --> 00:25:16.149
time, I need to keep

00:25:16.159 --> 00:25:18.390
walking down the road

00:25:18.390 --> 00:25:18.400
here."Or

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:20.710
would he go, "Hey,

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:22.950
you know what? I'd like to take my

00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:25.669
sandals off here and sit down

00:25:25.679 --> 00:25:28.870
and visit. Can we just have a little bit

00:25:28.880 --> 00:25:32.549
of tea? Let's have that iced

00:25:32.559 --> 00:25:36.070
tea, son. I'd like to sit down and talk.

00:25:36.080 --> 00:25:38.602
Just have a little talk with

00:25:38.612 --> 00:25:39.430
Jesus."So,

00:25:39.440 --> 00:25:41.830
I just try to inspire you all to

00:25:41.840 --> 00:25:44.630
get close to him before we get into

00:25:44.640 --> 00:25:46.470
the real serious stuff with Pam

00:25:46.480 --> 00:25:48.310
Bondi and all the things that the Lord

00:25:48.320 --> 00:25:51.110
has shown us. It all comes out of

00:25:51.120 --> 00:25:53.990
relationship.

00:25:54.000 --> 00:25:55.269
I'm going to be real with y'all: I have

00:25:55.279 --> 00:25:59.029
issues, Diana has issues, Braden

00:25:59.029 --> 00:25:59.039
has—we

00:25:59.039 --> 00:26:01.430
all have issues. But we

00:26:01.440 --> 00:26:05.350
diligently seek him. We want him more

00:26:05.360 --> 00:26:08.870
than we want air. I want him more than I

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:11.350
want water. I'm a big guy and I'm

00:26:11.360 --> 00:26:12.789
overweight, and I want him more than I

00:26:12.799 --> 00:26:16.630
want food. How much more

00:26:16.640 --> 00:26:18.390
do you want the Father in your life and

00:26:18.400 --> 00:26:21.510
change? I don't want to live tomorrow the

00:26:21.520 --> 00:26:24.230
same way

00:26:33.840 --> 00:26:35.909
I did today. I don't want to be this way

00:26:35.919 --> 00:26:39.350
this time next year. Smith Wigglesworth

00:26:39.360 --> 00:26:42.070
said, "If you don't see change in your

00:26:42.080 --> 00:26:44.630
life spiritually every three days,

00:26:44.640 --> 00:26:46.723
you're

00:26:46.723 --> 00:26:46.733
backsliding."That

00:26:46.733 --> 00:26:48.470
challenged me. I

00:26:48.480 --> 00:26:50.470
thought,

00:26:50.480 --> 00:26:52.870
