02:13:22.310 --> 02:13:22.320
a

02:13:22.320 --> 02:13:25.910
computer screen. It may look beautiful.

02:13:25.920 --> 02:13:27.669
But you have that still small voice on

02:13:27.679 --> 02:13:31.030
the inside of you that says, 'Don't do

02:13:31.040 --> 02:13:33.910
it.'Follow

02:13:33.920 --> 02:13:36.550
the peace that passes all

02:13:36.560 --> 02:13:39.189
understanding. The peace will lead you

02:13:39.199 --> 02:13:41.750
and guide you.

02:13:44.159 --> 02:13:46.069
He will lead you and guide you into all

02:13:46.079 --> 02:13:48.149
things, showing you what to do with your

02:13:48.159 --> 02:13:50.382
life. He is the Prince of Peace.

02:13:52.239 --> 02:13:57.350
If you have a check, don't do it,

02:13:57.360 --> 02:14:00.390
and you will always be blessed in what

02:14:00.400 --> 02:14:02.629
you do.

02:14:02.639 --> 02:14:04.709
Hallelujah. You say, 'If it's

02:14:04.719 --> 02:14:08.069
family or whatever, I don't care;

02:14:08.079 --> 02:14:12.629
if you don't have peace, don't do

02:14:12.629 --> 02:14:12.639
it.'That's

02:14:12.639 --> 02:14:14.950
what I go by every single

02:14:14.960 --> 02:14:16.870
time. I have a check, but I've always

02:14:16.880 --> 02:14:18.470
known the Holy Spirit is there to be my

02:14:18.480 --> 02:14:21.030
friend. He

02:14:21.030 --> 02:14:21.040
wants to

02:14:21.040 --> 02:14:23.430
help you. I don't care how good it

02:14:23.440 --> 02:14:25.830
looks,

02:14:25.840 --> 02:14:29.350
always follow the peace of God.

02:14:29.360 --> 02:14:32.550
No matter how it sounds, no matter how

02:14:32.560 --> 02:14:34.149
much they love you,

02:14:34.159 --> 02:14:40.817
I don't care.

02:14:41.679 --> 02:14:44.629
So, praise the Lord.

02:14:46.480 --> 02:14:48.310
We pray over President

02:14:48.320 --> 02:14:50.149
Trump's heart. We pray over his

02:14:50.159 --> 02:14:53.270
marriage. We pray over the kids.

02:14:53.280 --> 02:14:54.950
It's good, but

02:14:54.960 --> 02:14:57.270
there's still an underlying

02:14:57.280 --> 02:14:59.430
Braden.

02:14:59.440 --> 02:15:01.910
This is not a 'one and done.'This is to

02:15:01.920 --> 02:15:04.709
keep praying. We must pray for President

02:15:04.719 --> 02:15:07.109
Trump's organs,

02:15:07.119 --> 02:15:09.510
praying for his heart. This is a very

02:15:09.520 --> 02:15:12.149
stern warning.

02:15:12.159 --> 02:15:15.750
Pray for his life. Pray for him.

02:15:19.360 --> 02:15:21.270
Lord, I just release it. I've got

02:15:21.280 --> 02:15:23.030
a lot of prayer warrior mamas out there.

02:15:23.040 --> 02:15:25.030
I have Arkansas Grandma.

02:15:26.800 --> 02:15:28.310
She wrote me a letter today telling me

02:15:28.320 --> 02:15:30.790
she prayed for me.

02:15:30.800 --> 02:15:33.430
Arkansas Grandma was there. Amen. It

02:15:33.430 --> 02:15:33.440
was

02:15:33.440 --> 02:15:35.189
such a beautiful letter.

02:15:36.239 --> 02:15:38.310
It blessed us. She had a prophetic word

02:15:38.320 --> 02:15:40.310
for me.

02:15:40.320 --> 02:15:43.589
I said,

02:15:43.599 --> 02:15:46.790
'Thank you for praying for me,

02:15:46.800 --> 02:15:48.709
thank you for praying for my wife and my

02:15:48.719 --> 02:15:50.550
kids, Arkansas Grandma and these

02:15:50.560 --> 02:15:51.430
people.'Glory

02:15:51.440 --> 02:15:53.350
to God for these people,

02:15:53.360 --> 02:15:55.270
always praying and

02:15:55.280 --> 02:15:56.550
interceding.

02:15:56.550 --> 02:15:56.560
I

02:15:56.560 --> 02:15:58.229
don't know how old the grandma is, but

02:15:58.239 --> 02:15:59.750
it's just neat to have a grandma praying

02:15:59.760 --> 02:16:00.790
for you.

02:16:03.199 --> 02:16:04.069
Glory to God.

02:16:04.079 --> 02:16:05.270
Appreciate it so much.

02:16:11.840 --> 02:16:13.350
You have your assignments. You can help

02:16:13.360 --> 02:16:15.350
me pray until tomorrow. Tomorrow's

02:16:15.360 --> 02:16:17.510
Tuesday and we'll pray again. We'll keep

02:16:17.520 --> 02:16:19.189
praying until the Lord

02:16:19.189 --> 02:16:19.199
says...

02:16:19.199 --> 02:16:22.229
we

02:16:22.229 --> 02:16:22.239
are

02:16:22.239 --> 02:16:24.069
winners.

02:16:24.079 --> 02:16:24.950
We go through

02:16:24.960 --> 02:16:28.390
October 31st. We keep

02:16:28.400 --> 02:16:29.830
doing the things the Lord's

02:16:29.840 --> 02:16:32.389
called us to do. We've had 5,500

02:16:32.399 --> 02:16:34.070
people praying right now, and I believe

02:16:34.080 --> 02:16:36.549
with all my heart there's power, for many

02:16:36.559 --> 02:16:38.790
hands make light work.

02:16:38.800 --> 02:16:40.150
We're on the victory

02:16:40.160 --> 02:16:43.669
side. We love you all. Remember,

02:16:43.679 --> 02:16:46.870
put a smile on your face and a song in

02:16:46.880 --> 02:16:49.349
your heart. Jesus loves you so much and

02:16:49.359 --> 02:16:51.030
we love you. God bless you and we'll see

02:16:51.040 --> 02:16:54.840
you again soon. Bye-bye.

